{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sandbox Marble Track Creator</strong></h2> Create the marble track of your dreams with dozens of parts and in different environments. Build your marble track with slopes, pipes and curves or go a little more crazy and use triggers, elevators and boosters. If that's not enough then there are also teleporters, gravity fields and marble eaters.<br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/extras/ezgif-2-08c3dd8226.gif?t=1720169294\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mind bending Puzzles</strong></h2>Solve nifty puzzles created by our own team or by the community. Use the parts correctly to guide each marble to their goal. An ever increasing level of difficulty makes sure you get in easily and are challenged for a long time.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/extras/ezgif-4-fad9dced27.gif?t=1720169294\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Exciting Game Modes</strong></h2>Defend yourself against the marbles in tower defense mode. Make sure the marbles don't hit the detonation trigger and instead reach the goal.<br>Choose the right parts to build your deck and use your deck to solve increasingly difficult puzzles in rogue like mode. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/extras/ezgif-4-4ea5d081ca.gif?t=1720169294\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1720169294","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1720169294","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720169294","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332080/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1720169294","cat